title: Campos Foods, LLC Recalls Beef Products Due to Misbranding and Undeclared Allergens
summary: Editors note (Mar 4, 2015): This release is being reissued to include additional product and a change in the number of pounds being recalled. WASHINGTON, March 2, 2015 Campos Foods, LLC, a Caryville, Tenn. establishment, is recalling approximately 126,705 pounds of beef products due to...
